# Build folders
Debug/
Release/
Objects/
Listings/

# Keil build subfolders
MDK-ARM/Debug/
MDK-ARM/Release/
MDK-ARM/Objects/
MDK-ARM/Listings/

# ARM folders if present
ARM/Debug/
ARM/Release/
ARM/Objects/
ARM/Listings/

